    Package Description
    org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.nodemanager.containermanager.linux.runtime  
    org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.nodemanager.containermanager.linux.runtime.runc
    Package containing classes related to runC commands and common operations used within the @{link RuncContainerRuntime}.
  • Classes in org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.nodemanager.containermanager.linux.runtime.runc used by org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.nodemanager.containermanager.linux.runtime 
    Class and Description
    RuncContainerExecutorConfig
    This class is used by the RuncContainerRuntime to pass a JSON object to the container-executor.
    RuncImageTagToManifestPlugin
    This class is a plugin interface for the RuncContainerRuntime to convert image tags into OCI Image Manifests.
    RuncManifestToResourcesPlugin
    This class is a plugin interface for the RuncContainerRuntime that maps OCI Image Manifests into associated config and layers.
